                            <comment id="49375" author="liwei" created="Tue, 18 Dec 2012 08:13:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The work is being done by Yu Jian under &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1526&quot; title=&quot;interop 1.8,2.1 -&amp;gt; 2.4 &amp;quot;mkfs.lustre FATAL: The target index must be specified with --index&amp;quot;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1526&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1526&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.  I&apos;m marking this as a duplicate.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="42222" author="liwei" created="Tue, 24 Jul 2012 21:16:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have to pick a specific 2.1 release for &quot;affects version/s&quot;.  2.1.3 is probably too early.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="42221" author="liwei" created="Tue, 24 Jul 2012 21:13:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;b2_1 clients will need the patches landed to master under &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1415&quot; title=&quot;lustre-client-tests on the client must be modified to support Orion servers&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1415&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1415&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; as soon as we start interoperability testing between b2_1 and a newer version with OFD and ZFS OSD servers.  I&apos;m not sure if we are to test 2.1 clients withe 2.3 OFD-based OSSs, since OFD and ZFS OSD will be previews in 2.3.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m changing &quot;affects version/s&quot; to 2.1.  Please re-consider the priority.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="42207" author="jlevi" created="Tue, 24 Jul 2012 15:20:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We need clarification on what this problem is please.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
